Entry.JapaneseText: ペトナジャンカを離れてからずいぶん経ったな…… 姉貴、どうしてるかな……
Entry.EnglishText: It's been a long time since I left Petnadjanka... I wonder how my sister is doing...

Entry.JapaneseText: 元気にしてるんじゃないのぉ？
Entry.EnglishText: She should be doing well, you think?

Entry.JapaneseText: 元気にしてると思うか？ おれの事、心配してないかな？
Entry.EnglishText: You think she's doing well? You don't think she's worrying about me, do you?

Entry.JapaneseText: いや……そんなコト、ボクに聞かれても…… 本当、<Tytree>ってシスコンだよネ！
Entry.EnglishText: Well, I wouldn't be able to answer that... Man, <Tytree>, you really are a siscon!
It's called caring about your sister!
